posting_body: ['Ascend at Red Rocks', '13105 West 2nd Place, Lakewood, CO, 80228', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Welcome Home to Ascend at Red Rocks Apartment Homes', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 925 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Ascend at Red Rocks Apartment Homes offers spacious one, two, and three bedroom apartments nestled in the foothills of the Rocky Mountains.', 'Only minutes away from downtown Denver, the community is in close proximity to numerous parks, shopping destinations, restaurants, and entertainment.', 'Residents can enjoy a dip in the pool, take a stroll with their dog around the community or take a short drive to enjoy the nearby countryside.', 'Whether it’s the fast pace of city life or a relaxing mountain atmosphere you’re looking for, Ascend at Red Rocks Apartment Homes has something for everyone.', 'Features', '- Air Conditioning', '- Washer/Dryer', 'Community Amenities', '- Professional Management', '- Flexible Lease Terms Available', '- Fitness Center', '- Storage Space', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday:12:00PM-4:00PM', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 times the rent', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'lqSh3bHi2uTF']
